Eating Attitudes
Test (EAT-26)©
Instructions
This is a screening measure to
help you determine whether you
might have an eating disorder
that needs professional attention.
This screening measure is not
designed to make a diagnosis of
an eating disorder or take the
place of a professional consultation.
Please fill out the form below
as accurately, honestly and completely
as possible. There are no right
or wrong answers. All of your
responses are confidential.
